    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i feel like i'm already so tired that i won't even notice if i'm extra drowsy. isn't melatonin just a natural hormone and ambien is a medication, so they shouldn't really fight each other or anything? i just want them to work together so i can finally get a full night. wouldn't taking them together just make it more effective for the insomnia?",
